'''Drui''' is a dance practiced by the [[Kanak people]]s of [[New Caledonia]].<ref name="AmmannBecker1997">{{cite book|last1=Ammann|first1=Raymond|last2=Becker|first2=David|title=Kanak dance and music: ceremonial and intimate performance of the Melanesians of New Caledonia, historical and actual|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_f46AAAAMAAJ|accessdate=10 June 2011|year=1997|publisher=Agence de développement de la culture kanak|isbn=978-0-7103-0586-2|page=179}}</ref>

