'''Sastreria Cornejo S.A.''' is a company that specialises in costumes for film, television and theater. It is a Spanish company headquartered in [[Madrid]].<ref>http://www.info-empresas.net/Sastreria_Cornejo_Sa_emp-22930</ref> It was founded in 1920 by Humberto Cornejo.<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sastreriacornejo.com/esp/historia.asp# |title=Archived copy |access-date=3 December 2008 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20041028211417/http://www.sastreriacornejo.com/esp/historia.asp# |archive-date=28 October 2004 |dead-url=yes |df=dmy-all }}</ref>
